  <acronym>CONKO-101</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open Labeled Phase 2 Study of Gemcitabine in Combination With Cisplatin, 5-FU (24h CI) and Folinic Acid in Patients With Inoperable Esophageal Cancer</official_title>
